Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.34,0:00:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友情　恋爱　神秘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那样的约定的话就可以坚持到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,历史悠久充满怀旧气氛的古宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招揽游客时有发生事件的预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.24,0:00:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩  头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.19,0:02:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是鬼泽乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.69,0:02:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种好怀念从前的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.49,0:02:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫想愁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.89,0:02:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是乡愁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.39,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候换这个词了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.99,0:02:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂你们才几岁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.89,0:02:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个据说快成为地球遗产的村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是现在的话题焦点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可最近这里因其他热点而引起了关注
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.29,0:02:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,观光客也增加了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.89,0:02:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的那个其他的热点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.99,0:02:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们真是讨厌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是幽灵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.59,0:02:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在半年之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.19,0:03:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好几个人说看到过小孩子的幽灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.29,0:03:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是这个说法就这么传开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难得有人以此作为解决案子的谢礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.09,0:03:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招待我来这里旅游的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.69,0:03:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个好好感受充满历史氛围的日本啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不像话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可要享受啤酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.09,0:03:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱与幽灵与地球遗产（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越来越厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.39,0:03:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像回到了过去一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.39,0:03:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们住在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.59,0:03:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既是地球遗产又是可以投宿的民居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.79,0:03:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是历史悠久的日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有三层楼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房间数比从外面看上去要多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定以前是个大家族呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.79,0:04:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的地基石头和旁边的土都是新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.19,0:04:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是具有百年历史的老房子的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是和我们一起住的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.09,0:04:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.39,0:04:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最古老的传统式的家庭旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留美子真高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么破旧的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么破有洗澡的地方吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有空调呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是没有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.09,0:04:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被他听到的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.69,0:04:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要太过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不像话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要给别人添麻烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢说我是麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换了以前可饶不了你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是看不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁看不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.29,0:05:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.59,0:05:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.69,0:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡的小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迫不得已成为了名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说迫不得已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没听见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留美子太高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你可是名人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐们这样我的啤酒都洒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫坂木庄吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能见到您真是我的荣幸 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫桑岛和明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.89,0:05:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.99,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人您住的地方是隔壁的石冈先生那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛不早说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个石火锅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岩鱼也很鲜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香的酱汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝了后身体都暖和多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天喝这个最好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登这种乱七八糟的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里没有这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.89,0:06:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样对客人太失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.19,0:06:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近发生了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.59,0:06:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个啊 小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这篇报道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这本杂志怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球遗产村里有幽灵出没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经常出现给当地居民造成困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.49,0:06:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意外的卖点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.69,0:06:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵什么的根本没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽给我们添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.09,0:07:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球遗产是世界的骄傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.99,0:07:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是人类的财产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来就很了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.19,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这么伟大的地方搞什么捉鬼游戏真是不像话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作为这里的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该好好招待你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.99,0:07:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您真是金玉良言啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再敬一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.49,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.89,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.09,0:07:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南我们也差不多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢 睡觉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.49,0:08:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没确认是不是真的有幽灵之前是睡不着的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.39,0:08:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是为了这个才来的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.09,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回房间看书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.79,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去散步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么晚去散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不是很晚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个也是这里的特色啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.39,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火烛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火烛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.29,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.59,0:09:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算那个出来了也不是很奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.09,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上这里的人都轮流这样巡逻吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.29,0:09:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 火灾是茅草屋的大敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要互相提醒小心翼翼才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个村子的人都要负责提醒互相帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经成为惯例了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火烛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.99,0:09:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火烛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.49,0:09:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 步美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚还在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿她没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.59,0:09:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这里为止我们还在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.09,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是肚子饿了一个人先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又不是元太你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.39,0:10:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是步美的围巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.89,0:10:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要扔下我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.99,0:10:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.69,0:10:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们明明和她在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.29,0:10:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想还是大家一起找比较好所以就回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家分头去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.69,0:10:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.59,0:11:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家那位也是一沾上酒就停不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫村子里的人一起找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.89,0:11:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮忙哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.69,0:11:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是醉鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.29,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在水神庙的杉树这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么地方痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.39,0:12:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.59,0:12:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以说话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了一个女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10岁左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,童花头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿着红裙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.89,0:12:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.79,0:13:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.49,0:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是来找荣治的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.99,0:13:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫真美吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.29,0:13:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美和死去的荣治是青梅竹马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年龄只差一岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.99,0:13:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她相信荣治的清白所以来找他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.89,0:13:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.09,0:13:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹 是你看错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我确实看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你不相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.49,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美不是撒谎的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.09,0:13:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么说肯定是看错了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两人都已经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荣治在上个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩早在十年前都已经死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前就已经死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.19,0:14:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很害怕鬼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.39,0:14:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.39,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 惠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵什么呢 这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.19,0:14:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你真是的这种时候说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是受了谁的指使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.69,0:14:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.89,0:14:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那些家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会上你们的当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你们称心如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.19,0:14:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且荣治这种孩子不是我的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样荣治太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给您赔罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.89,0:15:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚才难得喝得那么痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点什么哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是幽灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.89,0:15:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.89,0:15:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有调查的价值了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.19,0:15:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是幽灵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乙泽家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.39,0:16:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是真美一家十年前住的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是独生女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.79,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是得病去世的吧 真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.49,0:16:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随后她的爸爸妈妈就搬到其他地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有留下照片什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了十年了不太可能了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉田看到的是不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到照片就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.79,0:16:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.29,0:16:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么真假 是说幽灵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么连你也这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.89,0:16:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.99,0:16:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是以理论和推理取胜的侦探啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没说这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.89,0:17:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个是在问你是不是不相信吉田的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.99,0:17:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记住 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是这个叫荣治的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.89,0:17:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个永仓荣治吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.09,0:17:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说在有关犯罪的报纸里查一查叫永仓荣治的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果查到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.09,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案子发生在半年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.59,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,净真町就是你们现在所在的鬼泽乡旁边的小镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.79,0:17:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现场的指纹分析出来后马上通缉了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕他是无路可逃了才自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.19,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永仓荣治是自杀的宝石强盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.79,0:18:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他妈妈相信儿子是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.09,0:18:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就知道为什么村里的人都守口如瓶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.89,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有撒谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.79,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.49,0:18:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望至少柯南一定要相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想让他调查是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.69,0:18:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样你就能安心的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰原你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.29,0:18:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江户川君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一路上怎么毛骨悚然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.59,0:18:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在刚才的地方碰到了真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.09,0:18:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是被她邀请来到了水神庙这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.09,0:18:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.89,0:18:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.79,0:19:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那以后就再也没有出现过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.09,0:19:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我叫真美叫累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在杉树的树根这里睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.49,0:19:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在哪里消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说准哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雾很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在那座水神庙的旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还很新呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.39,0:19:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玉井 是我们路过的家庭旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.39,0:19:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件浴袍被风吹得呼啦呼拉地动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后步美就看错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗完的衣服怎么会跑到这么远的地方来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.89,0:19:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有看错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.69,0:19:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定看到真美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.69,0:20:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你啊 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是偶然偶然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.19,0:20:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人到底在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火烛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.79,0:20:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火烛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁的脚步声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来了出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.59,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.09,0:20:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是幽灵是没有脚的啊元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们呆在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么就安静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最上面一层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.39,0:21:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.49,0:21:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.39,0:21:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.09,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.19,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.59,0:21:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人还没逃远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.19,0:21:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.09,0:21:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美你果然在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.89,0:21:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.78,0:23:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.84,0:23:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然承你这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.58,0:23:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下毛利小五郎就先拔头筹了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.77,0:23:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是幽灵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 柯南也看到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.60,0:24:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.38,0:24:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样 原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然真正的凶手是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.50,0:24:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概今晚就会出现在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.13,0:24:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.47,0:24:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱与幽灵与地球遗产（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.90,0:24:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放大镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.30,0:24:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次是解决篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.20,0:24:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是刚才是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.60,0:24:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害的人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.70,0:24:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.32,0:00:25.64,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,近日时常梦见你突然离我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.21,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,面对惶惑不安的我 你依然无声无息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.79,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一双温暖的手紧握在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.06,0:00:42.09,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,纠缠的五指仿佛缤纷的花朵竞色争奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.09,0:00:49.62,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,即使停驻于忧郁隐晦的霏霏霪雨 你的身影依然那么粲然夺目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.23,0:00:55.75,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,向着你我约定过的温柔之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.90,0:01:01.09,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,而今两个人依然齐肩攀越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.30,0:01:06.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,遥望你为我彩绘的梦幻季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.96,0:01:14.78,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,暂别的时日可以令爱更强烈 直至岁月翻过那一页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.16,0:01:20.78,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,向着你我约定过的温柔之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.89,0:01:25.86,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,无谓的逃避只会迷途无措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.39,0:01:31.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,纵然漫无标识的路千曲百折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.96,0:01:39.57,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1450)}依循彼此的信任与爱相携 直至步入那温柔世界…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.77,0:22:39.05,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的视线相遇之前 心就已经决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.63,0:22:49.29,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如同正午的月亮一般 虽然看不见 但是知道它在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.17,0:23:01.88,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是孤独 就算是幸福 一个人的时候又怎能分辨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.32,0:23:13.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的相遇 如同在深海中游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.06,0:23:26.41,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你沐浴在光芒下呼吸 寻找我们两人的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.64,0:23:38.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在围绕着升起又落下的太阳 旋转的这个星球上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.28,0:23:45.01,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧缓缓起伏的海面上的月亮
